&lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_logs/64716322-2c90-11e6-bbf5-5254006e85c2/show_text&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_logs/64716322-2c90-11e6-bbf5-5254006e85c2/show_text&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="141862" author="standan" created="Wed, 10 Feb 2016 22:03:06 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Another instance found for interop tag 2.7.66 - EL6.7 Server/2.7.1 Client, build# 3316&lt;br/&gt;
